From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 20:47:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] fix(security): stop exposing password hashes and full
 user docs

- User schema: password is now select:false; only the credentials
  authorize flow opts in via getUser(email, { withPassword: true })
- getUsers: typed role filter instead of raw FilterQuery (server actions
  are public endpoints callable with arbitrary args), field projection at
  the query, .lean() instead of serializing whole documents
- getUsersWithIds: same, plus teacher-only gate since it returns emails
